At this point, the Acting President Pro Tempore and Majority Leader (Council Member Cumbo) made the following declaration:

I now formally declare 
     the Executive Expense-Revenue-Contract Budget; 
     the Executive Capital Budget; 
     and the Community Development Program Budget
          for Fiscal Year 2019;
all as modified;
and all in accordance with the relevant sections 
of the New York City Charter; 
as hereby adopted

as of 4:40 p.m., on this 14th day of June, 2018.
